          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Admin10mm-Step-1-2-1686647050051-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a generous drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>roasted</strong> <strong>garlic paste </strong>and your <strong>bacon lardons</strong> and cook for 3-4 min or until the lardons are browned and crisped</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/R2338v2Step-2-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/R2338v2Step-2-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/R2338v2Step-2-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/R2338v2Step-2-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/R2338v2Step-2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the bacon is cooking, add your <strong>quick cook spaghetti</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook for 2-3 min or until the spaghetti is cooked with a slight bite then drain, reserving a cup of the <strong>starchy pasta water</strong> and return to the pot with a drizzle of<strong> olive oil</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/R2338v2Step-3-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/R2338v2Step-3-x400.jpg",
