    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>egg yolk[s]</strong> to a bowl with your <strong>crème fraîche</strong>, <strong>half </strong>your <strong>grated Italian hard cheese </strong>(you'll use the rest later!), your <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> and your <strong>cracked black pepper</strong></p><p>Stir it all together – this is your <strong>carbonara sauce</strong></p>",
