    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>tomato[es]</strong> roughly</p><p>Wash your <strong>salad</strong>, then pat dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Add the <strong>salad </strong>to a medium bowl with the <strong>chopped tomato</strong>, your <strong>balsamic vinegar </strong>and a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>– this is your <strong>tomato salad</strong></p>",
