    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the bacon lardons have browned, remove the pan from the heat and add the <strong>drained spaghetti</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>carbonara sauce</strong> with a splash of <strong>starchy pasta water </strong>and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>creamy spaghetti carbonara</strong></p><p>Tip: Mix the sauce through the pasta quickly to avoid scrambling the egg!</p>",
