      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>creamy spaghetti carbonara</strong> with the<strong> tomato salad</strong> to the side</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>remaining grated Italian hard cheese </strong>and a good grind of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
